name: Solar System (itch) (duck for mo)
description:
This is my Solar System project. I added the following elements:

  1. Mercury 
  2. Venus 
  3. Mars
  4. Jupiter 
  5. Saturn
  6. Uranus
  7. Neptun
  8. Pluto

All Planets have a rotation around themselve and around the sun. They also got 3D audio effects.

I hope you like my project :)
